MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '农业' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.opening_price AS temp MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE td.trade_data.opening_price <= temp RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND indus.industry.name == "农业" 
RETURN indus.industry.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE indus.industry.name == "农业" AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN indus.industry.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50
